  m_Name: Resident 2A
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  SpeakerName: 
  lines:
  - Whenever it gets windy you can hear a large sound by the front door.
  - "It feels like they didn\u2019t patch something up properly."
  - "I try to investigate myself but I can\u2019t find the source of the issue."
  - "Maybe you\u2019ll have better luck than me. "
